ta-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hololive_english_advent_image.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hololive_english_advent_image.jpg" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/hololive_english_advent_image.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-97521"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading"> Hololive英语2年来首次新人登场</h2><p>这位新人将是自 2021 年 8 月以来两年左右首次在 Hololive English 上亮相的新人。</p><p> 7月24日，该公司在该集团官方YouTube频道和Twitter官方账号上发布了一段“神秘视频”。除了确认了与7月3日举行的live活动“hololive英语第一场演唱会-Connect the World-”结束时发布的“神秘标志”视频相同的场景外，还出现了“多个神秘人物”。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【#holoAdvent】BREACH【hololive English】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/g5-VtyLYb2Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="IYw1y3Q4vq"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-mystery-video-released-announcement-for-july-26-at-12pm-jst/">Hololive英文“神秘视频”发布 7月26日12点公告也公布</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="《Holo Live英语“神秘视频”7月26日中午12点发布公告》 — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-mystery-video-released-announcement-for-july-26-at-12pm-jst/embed/#?secret=6K1BQOBLei#?secret=IYw1y3Q4vq" data-secret="IYw1y3Q4vq" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p> 5月12日，该公司在其财务业绩材料中宣布了截至2024年3月31日的财年的几位新人才的首次亮相。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="7xgaa7pcNU"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/cover-corporation-plans-to-debut-new-talents-for-vtuber-agency-hololive-production-within-the-fiscal-year-ending-march-2024/">封面公司 VTuber 办公室 Hololive 制作新人亮相计划于截至 2024 年 3 月的财年</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“封面VTuber Office Hololive Production新人出道计划于2024年3月” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/cover-corporation-plans-to-debut-new-talents-for-vtuber-agency-hololive-production-within-the-fiscal-year-ending-march-2024/embed/#?secret=aE768B1SFq#?secret=7xgaa7pcNU" data-secret="7xgaa7pcNU" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hololivetv/status/1684035821052231685" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc_dgpKRj1k66eVpHBZt3Dzoo9sewK6kmtp1v_L7Hh1rxEI6YhWXWCyNa4Brn9ypiBCzntiVtzvMk8HT02tG7XuH8_yUuh_VAXzRd9-M6fpFz6GRYxAbc1VzDIEuZpVl-163QW5RpRrvPars-C_a8Xb1=w1097-h837-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><div class="bhwqf64c0ba4856e99" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
